{"word":"G3114 - μακροθυμέω - makrothyméō - mak-roth-oo-meh'-o - Bear long","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μακροθυμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>makrothyméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mak-roth-oo-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bear long"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொறுமையாயிரு, சாந்தமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to persevere patiently and bravely"},{"paragraph":"2. to be patient"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/G3116 - μακροθυμώς - makrothymṓs - mak-roth-oo-moce'/3116\">G3116</a>; to <i>be long spirited</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>forbearing</i> or (subjectively) <i>patient:</i> - bear (suffer) long, be longsuffering, have (long) patience, be patient, patiently endure."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3114 - μακροθυμέω - makrothyméō - mak-roth-oo-meh'-o/3114\">G3114</a>, <a href=\"#/G3115 - μακροθυμία - makrothymía - mak-roth-oo-mee'-ah/3115\">G3115</a>, <a href=\"#/G3116 - μακροθυμώς - makrothymṓs - mak-roth-oo-moce'/3116\">G3116</a>"}]}